{"tid":49207,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【潛航器爭議】環時︰雖不在中國領海，但那裏離中國比離美國近","createTime":"2016-12-21T14:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T16:22:22.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b60a77b5f7f5694520520bba7a5676a61c8ca00c","tid":49207,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:08:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20161221/s00004/1482289766165SL4_C4A1EB1882A2A4F534A105AE2569DEC3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20161221%2Fs00004%2F1482289766165SL4_C4A1EB1882A2A4F534A105AE2569DEC3.jpg&h=937cb5e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國軍方昨日（21日）向美國交還上周取走的美方無人潛航器，事件暫時解決。《環球時報》發表社評分析「中美誰該反思」，文中批評美軍在中國周邊搜集情報，「不管符不符合國際法，都構成了對中國利益的實際損害」。<br />\n<br />\n社評題為＜潛航器事件解決，中美誰該反思＞，指中美軍方處理事件時都保持了克制，反映兩國政府雖然對南海局勢有不同認識，但雙方都願意以合作態度解決糾紛，惟美國一些媒體質疑美國軍方這次表現「太軟」，損害地區盟友對美國信心，更主張要求中國道歉。<br />\n<br />\n不過社評反駁，「要說情緒，中國社會的情緒要比美國那邊大得多」，因為在中國公眾看來，美方到中國周邊搞海洋情報是對中國國家安全的嚴重威脅，「事發地點雖不在中國領海，但那裏離中國比離美國近了不知多少倍。它（美國）應想到，中國人對那一帶發生什麼有更高關切度」。<br />\n<br />\n社評又說，中美交往不僅要符合「國際法」，還要盡量合情合理，「美軍在中國周邊大肆搜集情報，不管符不符合國際法，都構成了對中國利益的實際損害，這種搞到別人家門口的咄咄逼人是一目了然的」。<br />\n<br />\n社評續指，美方要很清楚它是這些糾紛中的「戰略進攻者」，中國則是「戰略防御者」，「美方在這樣的態勢下不能逼中方太甚，這是華盛頓無論有多大優勢都不能忘記的」。<br />\n<br />\n社評最後提到，亞太和平需要中美合作，「兩國的分歧愈多，雙方合作就愈重要」，認為中美官方必須表現出責任感，做和平與穩定的守護者。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161221/s00004/1482289278992\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161221%2Fs00004%2F1482289278992&d=XFwM8SeD6i6b6mmQRHAgMaEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=de352910\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161221%2Fs00004%2F1482289278992&h=663424ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161221/s00004/1482289278992</a>"},{"pid":"a1bb7e3841ee60d2d0b6982557d13cc2da812a9e","tid":49207,"uid":1523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:17:00.000Z","msg":"真係癡線"},{"pid":"5736cfd31ab9e148bd86dd007764089468173ab6","tid":49207,"uid":22313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:18:49.000Z","msg":"知唔知咩叫公海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a948511e995fd432eaa5c73b8ef19e6b6064cf5","tid":49207,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:20:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">軍國主義</span></span>"},{"pid":"01e31f3561194729094710621bab4ae3e763014a","tid":49207,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T15:46:22.000Z","msg":"同美國駐賓基地邊個近D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6054f7d99b864f073aeb236e64f747b99947828","tid":49207,"uid":32325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:06:14.000Z","msg":"一句講哂咪唔係你嘅領海囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n計遠近㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁你係南海度又畫到人地屋企門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f27975c01c97f25d5976d140b348e538383f48f","tid":49207,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:17:57.000Z","msg":"偷人野重咁撚惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f5d6dd00362ab80067a2bf351ac24b7b68aac4","tid":49207,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:22:22.000Z","msg":"支持中國開戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}